title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Sick Sikh.” [From an Associated Press pick-up from a local New Delhi newspaper, reporting a stricken soldier. Submitted by E.A. Livingston, Richmond Hill, New York.]
